Yes We Can</link></musical_composition>
</video>
</visual_communication>
</auditory_communication>
</song>
</music>
, a music video supporting <person wordnetid="100007846" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<senator wordnetid="110578471" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../366/534366.xml">
Barack Obama</link></senator>
</person>
, produced by <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../061/1982061.xml">
Will.I.Am</link>. Harper is a member of the Obama for America National Finance Committee <ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%225%22])">5</ref>.</p>
<p>

Hill Harper recently launched a social network ForRealSolutions.com aimed at encouraging solutions to some of society's challenges</p>
